{"title":"情绪二题","authors":["黄东成"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":12,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"情绪二题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄东成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遭了半辈子白眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人前总佝偻着腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头，压得低低。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根金针扎进穴位，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麻……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辣……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酸……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从这一天开始，尊严复苏病愈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于挺直了腰杆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头，高高扬起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赞不绝口："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！神医。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风停了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雾从角角落落漫出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"模糊了水晶体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玻璃球上蒙一层水珠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水珠化成雾气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将视线遮没。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见了花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绽放混沌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见了树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结出隔膜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山水城廓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都藏起了本来面目。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人与人面对面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看不清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说不清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有脚步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在大雾凄迷中踯躅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁可有风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来吧，猛烈的风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹散浓雾，景物"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方能在混沌中重新显出。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}